div.div: (h) App Core Bloc that needs to await the user authentication. It's initialized in the HomePage.
(m) App Core Bloc that must be initialized at the very creation of the app. It's initialized in main.dart.
(b) App Core Bloc that depends on the lifecycle of a Feature Bloc. It's initialized inside of that Feature Bloc.
(w) Feature Bloc that depends on the lifecycle of a widget. It's initialized inside of that widget.

* This flow shows the autologin navigation to HomePage. In case of no valid session is found in the app it will navigate to LoginPage and from there the user can navigate to HomePage after a successful authentication. Check mobile_flows.png - Initial Navigation tab to see the activity diagram of the initial navigation.
